>“git:<a href=\"https://github.com\">https://github.com</a>” 클릭 후 “편집”을 클릭한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1123px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200113001 3\"\n        title=\"20200113001 3\"\n        src=\"/static/82ff5ab3bb71708bc94c5c23000f8929/e751c/20200113001_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/82ff5ab3bb71708bc94c5c23000f8929/5a46d/20200113001_3.png 300w,\n/static/82ff5ab3bb71708bc94c5c23000f8929/0a47e/20200113001_3.png 600w,\n/static/82ff5ab3bb71708bc94c5c23000f8929/e751c/20200113001_3.png 1123w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1123px) 100vw, 1123px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>일반 자격 증명 편집 화면에서 사용자이름, 암호 변경 후 저장한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1124px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"20200113001 4\"\n        title=\"20200113001 4\"\n        src=\"/static/5bdff459ca127ab2785f67a3b01c7631/11b93/20200113001_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5bdff459ca127ab2785f67a3b01c7631/5a46d/20200113001_4.png 300w,\n/static/5bdff459ca127ab2785f67a3b01c7631/0a47e/20200113001_4.png 600w,\n/static/5bdff459ca127ab2785f67a3b01c7631/11b93/20200113001_4.png 1124w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1124px) 100vw, 1124px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>위와 같이 하면 조금은 번거롭지만 Github 계정을 변경 하면서 commit이 가능하다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"note\"><pre class=\"language-note\"><code class=\"language-note\">ssh key생성을 하여 관리하면 자격증명관리자에서 변경하지 않고 좀더 편하게 진행 할 수 있다.\nssh key방법은 다음 포스트에 작성하도록 하겠다.</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"github 멀티계정 사용하기 - 자격증명관리자","date":"November 04, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/git/github-멀티계정-사용하기---자격증명관리자/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/gulp.js/test1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Category Test1","category":"gulp.js","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/git/github-멀티계정-변경하기---ssh-key/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"github 멀티계정 변경하기 - ssh key","category":"git","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}